10_2701 eːkasmin dineː yAːjYavalkyaH yaTAːpUːrvam upadeːzavAːcanaM kurvan AːsI:t .
10_2702 janakamahAːrAːjaH anyeː RSayaH ca zradDayAː zrRNvantaH Aːsan.
10_2703 tadAː eːva kazcana vaquH DAːvan tatra AːgatavAːn .
10_2704 RRSI:n uktavAːn ca-BoːH BoːH RSayaH BavatAːM kuqI:rAːNi agninAː jvalanti santi iti .
10_2705 parantu tad zrutvAː api yAːjYavalkyaH upadeːzaM taTAː eːva anuvartitavAːn .
10_2706 tadAː sarveː api RRSayaH Jaqiti utTAːya tatra DAːvitavantaH .
10_2707 jvalataH kuqI:rAːt svI:yAːni daNxa-kamaNxalu-mRgacarmAːdI:ni vastUːni AːnI:tavantaH ca.
10_2708 itoː api upadeːzaH anuvartamAːnaH eːva AːsI:t .
10_2709 janaka-mahAːrAːjaH nizcalam upavizya zrRNvan AːsI:t.
10_2710 kiYcitakAːla anantaram anyaH kazcana tatra Aːgatya uktavAːn - praBoː! janakamahAːrAːja! miTilAːnagareː agnisparzaH jAːtaH asti .
10_2711 mahAːn anarTaH samBavati iti .
10_2712 parantu tad zrutvAː api janakamahAːrAːjaH kiYcid api vicalitaH na aBavat .
10_2713 saH yaTAːpUːrvam upadeːzaM zrRNvan eːva AːsI:t .
10_2714 tataH kiYcit kAːla anantaram aparaH Aːgatya uktavAːn- mahAːrAːja! aDunAː tu rAːjaBavanam api agninAː jvalati.
10_2715 BavataH antaHpuram api dahyamAːnam asti iti.
10_2716 aDunAː api janakamahAːrAːjaH avicalitaH san upadeːzazravaNeː eːva nirataH AːsI:t .
10_2717 tat pazcAːt yAːjYavalkyaH upadeːzaM samAːpitavAːn .
10_2718 tataH anyAːn RSI:n uktavAːn ca - BoːH RSayaH! kuqI:raM jvalati iti vAːrtAːM zrRtvAː viraktAːH api BavantaH tatra DAːvitvAː svI:yAːni vastUːni AːnI:tavantaH .
10_2719 parantu janakamahAːrAːjaH svasya nagaraM , Bavanam antaHpuraM ca jvalati iti vAːrtAːM zrutvAː api kiYcit api vicalitaH na aBavat .
10_2720 BavatAːM tasya ca eːtAːvAːn eːva BeːdaH .
10_2721 ataH eːva ahaM tasya Aːgamana anantaram eːva upadeːzasya AːramBaM karoːmi iti .
10_2722 sarveː RSayaH lajjayAː natamastakAːH aBavan mUːrKaH zazakaH.
10_2723 eːkasmina vaneː eːkaH zazakaH AːsI:t .
10_2724 eːkadAː saH vRkSasya CAːyAːyAːM zayitaH AːsI:t .
10_2725 vRkSAːt eːkaM PalaM tasya mastakeː apatat .
10_2726 zazakasya nidrAː BagnAːBavat .
10_2727 saH acintayat - AːkAːzaH apatat .
10_2728 BayAːt kAːtaraH saH AːtmarakSaNAːya aDAːvat .
10_2729 mAːrgeː eːkaH vAːnaraH tamapazyat .
10_2730 vAːnaraH tam apRcCat - mitra ! kaTaM tvaM DAːvasi .
10_2731 zazakaH avadat- AːkAːzaH patati, ataH ahaM DAːvAːmi .
10_2732 BayAːt kAːtaraH vAːnaroː$pi aDAːvat .
10_2733 eːvaM vAːnaraM dRSqvAː mRgaH , mRgaM dRSqvAː gajaH, ityeːvaM krameːNa anyeː pazavoː$pi aDAːvan .
10_2734 mAːrgeː eːkaH zrRgAːlaH AːgacCati sma .
10_2735 saH gajaM pRSqavAːn -BavAːn kaTaM DAːvati .
10_2736 gajaH mRgam, mRgaH vAːnaram, ityeːvaM krameːNa anteː zazakaM sarveː pRSqvantaH .
10_2737 soː$vadat-AːkAːzaH patati .
10_2738 zrRgAːlaH taM pRSqavAːn-kutra AːkAːzaH patati.
10_2739 zazakaH tAːn sarvAːn tatrAːnayat yatra saH zayitaH AːsI:t .
10_2740 tatra patitaM PalaM sarveː apazyan .
10_2741 zrRgAːlaH taM zazakam avadat-areː mUːrKa! eːtat Palameːva vRkSAːt apatat na tu AːkAːzaH .
10_2742 sarveː pazavaH ahasan .
10_2743 zazakaH lajjitaH aBavat .
10_2744 kRSNacandraH nAːma kazcit AːsI:t.
10_2745 saH rupavAːn mahAːDanikaH ca .
10_2746 dEːveːna tasmEː sarvaM dattam AːsI:t.
10_2747 sundarI: guNavatI: ca BAːryAː, uttamaH santAːnaH,priyatamAːH bAːnDavAːH,guNavantaH suhRdaH ca tasya Aːsan.
10_2748 taTAːpi tasya pUːrNAː santuSqiH na AːsI:t.
10_2749 mama pAːrzveː sarvam asti .
10_2750 ataH BAːgyavAːn asmi eːva .
10_2751 parantu kim eːtAːni sarvAːNi nirantaraM mama eːva BaviSyanti .
10_2752 yadi kadAːcit mama BAːgyaM kSI:NaM BaviSyati tarhi kaTam ahaM jI:veːyam.
10_2753 api ca ,AːgAːmini janmani api idam eːva gRhaM, kSeːtraM,kuqumbaM,BAːryAː,putrAːH ca kiM mama BaveːyuH.
10_2754 eːtasyAːH samasyAːyAːH parihAːraH kaH.
10_2755 iti vicAːraH tam ahoːrAːtraM bAːDateː sma.
10_2756 yat yaM vAː saH pazyati tasya viSayeː cintayati-eːtada eːSaH vAː sarvadAː kiM mama eːva BaviSyati
10_2757 eːteːna Boːjaneː tasya ruciH vinaSqAː.
10_2758 nidrAː api dUːraM gatAː.
10_2759 eːkasmin dineː cittazAːnti arTaM saH mandiraM gatavAːn .
10_2760 tatra pravacanakartAː kazcit pravacanaM kurvan AːsI:t .
10_2761 saH avadat- BUːloːkeː sarvam anityam deːvAːH amRtasya seːvanAːt ciraYjI:vinaH nityasuKinaH ca Bavanti iti.
10_2762 idaM vacanaM kRSNacandrasya zroːtrayoːH patitam.
10_2763 tasya manasi upAːyaH kazcana utpannaH.
10_2764 yadi ahaM mat kuqumbajanAːH ca amRtaM seːveːmahi tarhi vayam api nityasuKina: BavituM zaknuyAːm Kalu.
10_2765 ataH saH nirNI:tavAːn yat mayAː indradarzanAːrTaM tapa: karaNI:yam iti.
10_2766 anantaradineː eːva saH samI:pasTaM vanaM gatavAːn .
10_2767 vaneː kutracit sTitvAː sarvAːNi suKAːni tyaktvAː kaVoːreː tapasi magnaH aBavat.
10_2768 eːteːna santuSqaH deːveːndraH kRSNacandrasya purataH pratyakSaH aBavat.
10_2769 amRtapUːrNaM Gaqam eːkaM tasmEː dattvAː saH - heː kRSNacandra ! BavantaH AːtRpti amRtaM pAːtum arhanti .
10_2770 parantu eːkaH niyamaH smartavyaH yat eːSaH GaqaH aDaH na sTAːpanI:yaH iti uktvAː antarhitaH jAːtaH.
10_2771 yadAː vanasya maDyaBAːgaH atI:taH tadAː .
10_2772 kRSNacandreːNa zOːcazawkAː prAːptAː .
10_2773 taxAːgaH kazcana teːna samI:peː dRSqaH.
10_2774 amRtaGaqaM kiM karoːmi.
10_2775 iti cintayan eːva saH paritaH dRSqiM prasAːritavAːn .
10_2776 tAːvatAː daridraH janaH kazcana tatra AːgatavAːn .
10_2777 kRSNacandraH kuyuktiM cintayan tasya samI:paM gatvAː- eːSaH viSapUːrNaH GaqaH .
10_2778 aDaH na sTAːpanI:yaH eːSaH.
10_2779 ataH yAːvat aham eːtasmin taxAːgeː snAːna AːdikaM kRtvAː prati AːgamiSyAːmi tAːvat BavatAː hasteːna eːva GaqaM gRhI:tvAː atra eːva sTAːtavyam iti uktvAː GaqaM tasya hasteː sTAːpayitvAː taxAːgaM gatavAːn.
10_2780 AːgataH manuSyaH tu atidaridraH udyoːgaH koː api na AːsI:t tasya .
10_2781 keːByazcit dineːByaH udaraveːdanAː api taM bahuDAː pI:xayati sma .
10_2782 vEːdyaM draSqum, OːSaDaM kreːtuM vAː tasya samI:peː Danam api na AːsI:t .
10_2783 jI:vaneː viraktiM prAːptavAːn saH loːkeː mAːdRzasya jI:vanam asAːDyam.
10_2784 mama maraNam eːva ucitam iti nizcitya viSapadAːrTasya anveːSaNAːrTam eːva vanaM praviSqavAːn AːsI:t .
10_2785 akasmAːt kRSNacandreːNa dattaH viSaGaqaH amRtaGaqaHiva tasmEː pratI:yata .
10_2786 saH Jaqiti Gaqam udGAːqaya viSaM pI:tavAːn.
10_2787 teːna kI:dRzaM PalaM prAːptaM iti punaH vaktavyaM na asti Kalu.
10_2788 yasya budDirbalaM tasya
10_2789 moːhana ! AːgacCa putra ! Boːjaneː vilambaH Bavati ! roːhiNI: aBavat .
10_2790 AːgacCAːmi mAːtaH ! idAːnI:M keːzaveːna saha kiYcit sandeːzavinimayaM karoːmi, moːhanaH uttaraM dattavAːn .
10_2791 putra ! keːzavastu ameːrikAːyAːM nivasati .
10_2792 Aːm matah ! idAːnI:m inqaraneːqa- mAːDyameːna AːvayoːH samparkaH asti .
10_2793 samprati sawgaNakeːna sampreːSitaH sandeːzaH kSaNeːnEːva saptasamudrasya pAːraM yAːti .
10_2794 eːtAːdRzam asti AːDunikaM jI:vanam ! asya sawgaNaka-yantrasya AːviSkAːreːNa udyoːgaH, zikSAː, manoːraYjanAːdi sarveːSu kSeːtreːSu vikAːsaH jAːtaH .
10_2795 satyaM dUːraBAːSa-vAːyuyAːnAːdiBiH dUːrasTasya saMsAːraH samI:pam AːyAːti, param iNqaraneːqamAːDyameːna tu aDunAː vasuDAː eːva kuqumbakaM jAːtam .
10_2796 dUːradarzanasya AːviSkAːreːNa aDunAː sarvasAːDAːraNAːH sarvAːn kAːryakramAːn dRzyAːn ca pazyanti .
10_2797 vidyutAː laByateː prakAːzaH vAːyuzca .
10_2798 gEːsa-inDanam, tAːpakaraNam, zI:takam ityAːdI:ni nAːnAːviDAːni vEːjYAːnikoːpakaraNAːni AːDunikaM jI:vanaM saMvarDayanti .
10_2799 ahoː ! vijYAːnasya camatkAːraH sarveːSu kSeːtreːSu dRzyateː .
10_2800 Bavatu himAːlayasya sarvoːccaziKaram aTavAː prazAːntamahAːsAːgarasya gAːmBI:ryam, atidUːrasTaH mawgalagrahaH Bavatu aTavAː mAːnavoːdarasTaH sUːkSmakI:qaH -sarvam idAːnI:M draSquM jYAːtuM ca zakyateː .
10_2801 vijYAːnasya eːteːna bahuviDeːna vikAːseːna saMsAːrasya sarveː prAːNinaH lAːBAːnvitAːH Bavanti .
10_2802 paraM vijYAːnasya upayoːgaH loːkakalyAːNAːya eːva kartavyaH, na tu vinAːzAːya .
10_2803 vidyAːyAːH budDiruttamAː.
10_2804 kasmiMzcit sTAːneː catvAːroː brAːhmaNakumAːrAːH parasparaM mitraBAːveːna vasanti sma .
10_2805 teːSAːM trayaH zAːstreːSu pAːrawgatAːH parantu budDirahitAːH Aːsan .
10_2806 eːkastu budDimAːn, keːvalaM zAːstravimuKaH .
10_2807 eːkadAː teː acintayan - kaH guNaH vidyAːyAːH yeːna deːzAːntaraM gatvAː DanAːrjanaM na kRtam .
10_2808 tat vayaM pUːrvadeːzaM caleːma .
10_2809 taTAː kRteː mAːrgeː jyeːSVaH avadat- ahoː ! asmAːkaM eːkaH caturTaH zAːstravimuKaH, keːvalaM budDimAːn .
10_2810 na tu DanAːdikaM laByateː vidyAːM vinAː .
10_2811 tat saH gacCatu gRham .
10_2812 eːtasya paraM dvitI:yaH avadat- eːvaM kartum ucitaM na Bavati, yataH eːSaH asmAːkaM ciramitram .
10_2813 ata eːva, AːgacCa mitra ! asmadupAːrjitasya vittasya samaBAːgI: BaviSyasi .
10_2814 eːkasmin vaneː mRtasiMhasya asTI:ni dRSqavantaH .
10_2815 tadAː praTamaH avadat- ahoː ! adya vidyAːyAːH parI:kSAː kartavyAː .
10_2816 ayaM siMhaH mRtaH tiSVati .
10_2817 asmEː siMhAːya jI:vanadAːnaM dAːtavyam .
10_2818 ityuktvAː saH siMhasya asTI:ni saMyoːjitavAːn .
10_2819 dvitI:yaH teːSu carma-mAːsaM-ruDiraM saMyoːjayati .
10_2820 tRtI:yaH yAːvat jI:vanaM saYcAːrayitum udyuktaH tAːvat caturTaH subudDiH uccEːH akaTayat - Boː mitra ! tiSVatu .
10_2821 yadi eːSaH jI:vati tahi sarveː vayaM mRtyumuKeː gamiSyAːmaH .
10_2822 tataH tRtI:yaH avadat - Dik mUːrKa ! ahaM vidyAːM niSPalAː na kariSyAːmi .
10_2823 subudDiH pratyavadat-yadi eːvam tadAː kSaNaM tiSVa yAːvat ahaM vRkSam AːroːhAːmi .
10_2824 ataH paraM yAːvat siMhaH sajI:vaH kRtaH tAːvat utTAːya saH tAːn trI:n api kumAːrAːn hatavantaH .
10_2825 zAːstravimuKaH subudDizca vRkSAːt avatI:rya gRhaM gataH .
10_2826 kasmin-cit vaneː BAːsurakaH nAːma siMhaH avasat .
10_2827 saH prati-dinam aneːkeːSAːm pazUːnAːm vaDam akaroːt .
10_2828 eːkadAː vanasya sarveː pazavaH tasya samI:pam agacCan avadan ca- mRgeːndra ! tvam kimarTam pazUːnAːm vaDam karoːSi .
10_2829 yadi eːkeːnEːva pazunAː tava tRptiH Bavati vayam svayam eːva tava BoːjanAːya prati-dinam eːkam pazum preːSayiSyAːmaH .
10_2830 teːSAːm vacanAːni zrutvAː BAːsurakaH avadat- yadi yUːyam eːvam vadaTa tarhi Bavatu taTAː .
10_2831 parantu yadi kasmin-cit divaseː mama BoːjanAːya eːkaH pazuH na AːgamiSyati tahi sarveːSAːm pazUːnAːm vaDam kariSyAːmi .
10_2832 tataH praBRti prati-dinam eːkaH pazuH siMhasya BoːjanAːya tasya samI:pam agacCat .
10_2833 saH acintayat- yadi mama maraNam nizcitam asti tahi aham mandam mandam gacCAːmi .
10_2834 saH zazakaH smAːrgeː eːkam kUːpam apazyat .
10_2835 tasmin kUːpeː sva-pratibimbam dRSqvAː saH eːkam upAːyam acintayat .
10_2836 kSuDAː-pI:xitaH BAːsurakaH tam dRSqvAː krudDaH aBavat apRcCat ca- kimarTam tvam vilambeːna AːgataH asi .
10_2837 prAːtaH aham avaSyam eːva sarveːSAːm pazUːnAːm vaDam kariSyAːmi .
10_2838 zazakaH vinayeːna avadat- mRgarAːja ! atra mama anyeːSAːm pazUːnAːm ca doːSaH na asti .
10_2839 aham tu paYca-zazakEːH saha tava samI:peː Aːgantum pravRttaH Aːsam .
10_2840 param mAːrgeː eːkaH aparaH siMhaH asmAːn amilat avadat ca- aham asya vanasya nRpaH asmi .
10_2841 ataH aham yuSmAːn BakSayiSyAːmi .
10_2842 aham tam avadam- asya vanasya nRpaH tu BasurakaH nAːma siMhaH asti .
10_2843 eːteːat zrutvAː saH siMhaH ati krudDaH aBavat .
10_2844 aham tu punaH AːgamiSyAːmi iti zapaTaM kRtvAː atra AːgataH asmi .
10_2845 eːtat AːkarNya BAːsurakaH kroːDeːna avadat- saH aparaH siMhaH kutra vasati .
10_2846 tam zI:Gram mahyam darzaya .
10_2847 tadAː saH zazakaH BAːsurakam eːkasya kUːpasya samI:peː anayat akaTayat ca- asmin kUːpeː saH siMhaH vasati .
10_2848 BAːsurakaH tasmin kUːpeː sva-rpatibimbam dRSqvAː ayam aparaH siMhaH iti matvAː uccEːH agarjat .
10_2849 sva-zabdasya prati-Dvanim zrutvAː tasmin kUːpeː akUːrdat rpAːNAːn ca atyajat .
10_2850 budDiH yasya balam tasya nirbudDeːH tu kutaH balam .
10_2851 pazya siMhaH mada-unmattaH zazakeːna nipAːtitaH .
10_2852 BAːratam RtunAːM deːzoː$sti .
10_2853 atra Sax Rtavoː Bavanti - grI:SmaH, varSAːH, zarad, heːmantaH, ziziraH vasantazca .
10_2854 varSAː-RtuH grI:SmAːt anantaram AːgacCati .
10_2855 eːtasya kalaH julAːI: mAːsataH sitambaramAːsaparyantaM Bavati .
10_2856 zrAːvaNa - BAːdrOː ca asya BAːratI:yOː mAːsOː staH .
10_2857 grI:Smasya tAːpeːna santaptAː pRTivI: varSAːyAːH Aːgamaneːna zI:talAː zAːntAː ca Bavati .
10_2858 AːkAːzaH kRSNEːH meːGEːH AːcCannaH Bavati .
10_2859 meːGeːSu vidyut prakAːzateː .
10_2860 meːGAːH garjanti .
10_2861 vRSqijaleːna nadyaH, taxAːgAːH kUːpAːzca pUːritAːH Bavanti .
10_2862 pRTivI: haritEːrGAːsEːH AːcCaditAː Bavati .
10_2863 vRkSeːSu latAːsu ca navI:nAːni patrAːNi AːgacCanti .
10_2864 prakRtiH zoːBanAː nAːrI:va zoːBateː .
10_2865 mayUːrAːH meːGAːn dRSqvAː nRtyanti .
10_2866 maNxUːkAːzca kUːrdanti raqanti ca .
10_2867 varSAːkAːlaH atI:va lAːBadAːyakoː$sti .
10_2868 asmAːkaM deːzasya kRSiH muKyataH varSAːjalam Aːzrayati .
10_2869 uttamayAː varSayAː uttamAː kRSirBavati .
10_2870 asmin RtOː zrI:kRSNa-janmAːSqamI:, rakSAːbanDanam, svatantratAːdivasAːdayaH utsavAːH AːyoːjitAːH Bavanti .
10_2871 varSAːkAːlasya kAːzcita hAːnayoː$pi samBavanti .
10_2872 eːtasmin kAːleː bahavoː mAːrgAːH jalamagnAːH kardamayuktAːzca.
10_2873 ativRSqeːH kAːraNeːna aneːkAːsu nadI:Su jalavRdDiH Bavati .
