3_826 gOːtamasya tapasyAː eːva balI:yasI: ,uta yazoːDarAːyAːH .
3_827 gOːtamaH buDdtvam prAːpya saMsAːreː pratiSVitaH sarvaviditazca aBavat .
3_828 kintu sAː yazoːDarAː eːSAː vasuDAː .
3_829 kSaNaM kSaNaM yAː saMsAːreː tapa AːcarantI: asti ,tasyAːH kAː pratiSVAː syAːt parivAːreː ,svajaneːSu,saMsAːreː ca .
3_830 koː vAː pratiSVAːM dadyAːt .
3_831 pratiSVAːyAːstu anyAː kaTAː ,pratizvasanam eːSAː kaTaM jI:vati, putraM jI:vayati, kaTam AːtmAːnaM rakSati iti cintanamAːtreːNa eːva mama zarI:reː kazcana kampaH sahatvaM sAːkSAːtkRtamiva anuButavAːn aham .
3_832 akasmAːt mama muKAːt niHsRtam- DanyAː tvaM vasuDeː tuByaM koːqizaH namaH .
3_833 mama kAːrayAːnacAːlakaH akasmAːt mama DvaniM zrutvAː samamBraM pRSqavAːn - kiM svAːmin .
3_834 mayAː uktaM nahi kiYcit .
3_835 kim iti duraBAːSazabdeːna upamaNxalAːDikAːriNaH prakoːSVaH zabdAːyamAːnaH jAːtaH .
3_836 aByAːsabaleːna dakSiNeːna hasteːna aDikAːrI: DvanigrAːhikam utTAːpya uktavAːn hariH oːtriNim aham upamaNxalAːDikAːrI: vadan asmi iti .
3_837 zrI:man namaskAːraH ahaM rAːjakI:ya - mahAːvidyAːlayasya zikSakakarmakarasawsya sacivaH vadan asmi - pratipakSataH uttaram AːyAːti .
3_838 namaskAːraH ,vadatu upamaNxalAːDikAːrI: aBAːSat.
3_839 mahAːzaya duHKeːna BavantaM sUːcayAːmi yat saH bAːlakaH mRtaH asti .
