4_1044 sarvakAːreːNa saMskRtasya saMvarDanaM karaNI:yam iti Aːdideːza uccanyAːyAːlayaH.
4_1045 mahAːvidyAːlaya saMskRtaM pramuKaviSayeː tveːna paVatAːM CAːtrAːNAːm saMKyAː prativarSaM nyunAː Bavati .
4_1046 eːtam eːva aMzaM nimittI:kRtya mahAːvidyAːlayeː saMskRta viBAːgasya piDAːnaM CAːtrAːNAːM, zikSikAːNAːM, samAːjasya vAː hitAːya na Baveːt iti mumbayI:yasya uccanyAːyAːlayasya nyAːyamurtiH xAː.
4_1047 DanaYjaya candracUːxavaryaH sUːvI:yaM nirNayam zrAːvita-vAːn eːSu dineːSu .
4_1048 mahAːvidyAːlaya snAːtakakSyAːyAːM praTameː varSeː saMskRtaM muKyaviSayeː tveːna paVantaH paYcadaza CAːtrAːH BaveːyuH .
4_1049 yadi CAːtrAːNAːM sawKayAː tatoː$pi nyunAːH Bavati tarhi saMskRta prAːDyAːpakasya veːtanasya kRteː kRteː mahAːvidyAːlayaH sarvakAːrI:yaM anudAːnaM na prAːpnoːti .
4_1050 ataH tAːdRzeː prasawgeː mahAːvidyAːlayaH sarvakAːrI:yaMsya anudAːnasya aBAːvAːt,veːtanaM dAːtuM mahAːvidyAːlayasya anicCAːtaH ca saMskRta aDyAːpakaH padAːt cyutaH Bavati .
4_1051 grAːma parI:sareː tu paYcaSAːH eːva saMskRtAːnurAːgiNaH saMskRteː paVitum icCanti .
