4_1055 vEːzAːlI: dAːbakeː, tasmin mahAːvidyAːlayeː eːkamnavanavaSaq tameː varSeː vyAːKyAːtrI: rupeːNa niyuktAː jAːtAː .
4_1056 kintu agreː CAːtrasawKayAːyAːH nyUːnatAːM nimittI:kRtya tasyAːH.
4_1057 sTiraniyuktiH nirAːkRtAː mahAːvidyAːlayeːna .
4_1058 mahAːvidyAːlayeːna nyAːyAːDikareːna CAːtrasawKayAː nyunatAːM manasi kurvatAː mahAːvidyAːlayI:yaH pakSaH eːva samarTitaH .
4_1059 tataH viSayoː$yam ucca nyAːyAːlayaM prati nI:taH .
4_1060 eːtAːdRzyAːM sTitOː sarvakAːraH eːva saMskRta viSayeː udAːravAːdI: Baveːt iti mumbayI:reːna uccanyAːyAːlayeːna svAːBiprAːyaH prakaqitaH .
4_1061 DanaM sarvakAːrasamipeː nAːsti .
