4_945 cAːlakaH yadAː samAːyAːtaH tadAː patraM DanaYca datvAː tam AːdiSqavAːn -teːna saciveːna saha mRtabAːlakasya gRhaM prati gatvAː AːgacCtu iti cAːlakaH gatavAːn .
