4_948 aDikAːrI: patraM paVitavAːn -DarmAːvatAːreːNa upamaNxalAːDikAːrI:mahoːdayeːna dattaM DanaM svI:kRtam .
4_949 parantu aneːneː Daneːna mahAːvidyAːlayasya purataH gatiroːDakasya nirmAːNAːrTaM BavataH samakSam asya aDamasya hAːrdikaH anuroːDaH asti iti .
4_950 alaM vistareːNa BavataH kRpAːBilAːSI:.
4_951 tasya hastataH patraM patitam .
4_952 nayaneː udveːgastimiteː AːstAːm.
4_953 na nI:yateː sUːcI: api dibanDu bAːla moːdinI: .
4_954 lAːhoːranagareː pUːrvaM dulI:candaH nAːma koːqyaDipatiH DanikaH nivasati sma .
4_955 svasya Danikatvasya viSayeː mahAːn garvaH tasya .
4_956 tasya sampattiH viMzatikoːqimitAː AːsI:t .
4_957 eːtat dyoːtayituM saH svasya gRhasya purataH viMzatiM patAːkAːH uxxAːyayati sma .
4_958 kadAːcit teːna zrutaM yat gurunAːnakaH lAːhoːra nagaram Aːgatya DarmazAːlAːyAːM kasyAːYcit vasati iti .
4_959 dulI:candaH tasya darzanAːrTaM gatavAːn .
4_960 tasya purataH suvarNamudrAːgranTiM kaYcit saMsTAːpya saH avadat -guruvarya kAː anyAː seːvAː mayAː karaNiyAː .
4_961 AːdeːSqavyaH aham iti .
4_962 gurunAːnakaH darzanamAːtreːNa eːva avagatavAːn yat eːtasya DanamadaH aDikaH asti iti .
4_963 ataH saH eːkAːM sUːcI:m AːnAːyya tasmEː dttva avadat - agrimeː janmani eːtat prtyarpaNiyaM BavatAː iti .
4_964 dilicandaH tAːM sUːcI:M guruprasAːdaM BAːvayan svagRhaM pratyAːgatavAːn , tAːM sUːcI:M pUːjAːgRheː BaktayAː sTAːpitavAːn ca .
4_965 kiYcit kAːlAːnantaraM tasya manasi vicAːraH AːgataH agrimeː janmani sUːcI: pratyarpaNI:yAː iti guruNAː sUːcitam .
4_966 kaTam eːtat zakyeːt .
4_967 maraNa samayeː kiM koː$pi AːtmanAː saha sUːcyAːdi vastu neːtum arheːt.
4_968 ataH saH tasmin eːva kSaNeː gurunAːnakasamI:pam Aːgatya avadat -kiYcit kAːlAːt purvaM BavatAː mahyam eːkAːM sUːcI:M dattvAː uktam AːsI:t yat eːSAː agrimeː janmani pratyarpaNI:yAː iti .
4_969 eːtat kaTaM vAː zakyeːt .
4_970 maraNa samayeː koː$pi kimapi neːtuM na zaknoːti Kalu .
4_971 tadAː gurunAːnkaH apRcCat -dulI:candaH maraNasamayeː yeːna eːkAː sUːcI: api neːtum na zakyateː saH BavAːn svasya samagrAːM sanpattiM kiM neːtuM na zaknuyAːt .
4_972 eːtAːni vacAːnAːni zrutavati dulI:candeː jYAːnasya udayaH jAːtaH .
4_973 saH gRhaM pratyAːgatya svasya sampateːH dAːnam AːrabDavAːn .
4_974 arheːByaH DanakanakAːdikaM datvAː saH gurunAːnakasya paramaBaktaH jAːtaH .
4_975 kasmiMzcit grAːmeː kazcana vaNik nivasati sma .
4_976 saH atyantaM caturaH .
4_977 kadAːcit saH gRheː upavEːzya nAːNakAːnigaNayan AːsI:t .
4_978 tadAː eːva mAːrgeː gacgCan kazcana coːraH tad dRSqavAːn .
4_979 saH manasi eːva cintitavAːn yat -eːtasya vaNijaH samipeː bahu Danam asti .
4_980 adya rAːtrOː mayAː eːtasmAːt gRhAːt eːva coːraNI:yam iti .
4_981 mAːrgeː sTitvAː cintayantaM coːram akasmAːt vaNik api dRSqavAːn .
4_982 tasya manasi saMzayaH utpannaH .
4_983 eːSaH manuSyaH coːraH eːva syAːt .
4_984 adya rAːtrOː eːSaH mama gRhameːva AːgacaCati iti dRXa nizcayaH sa patnI:m AːhUːya zanEːH uktavAːn -BavatI: adya rAːtrOː ucca svareːNa mAːM -BavAːn DanaM sarvaM kutra sTAːpitavAːn asti .
4_985 nagareː idAːnI:M coːraBI:tiH varDamAːnAː asti iti vadatu iti .
4_986 tataH vaNik eːkasmin Gateː kAːMzcit vRzcikAːn sTAːpayitvAː Gaqasya muKaM vastreːNa piDAːya GaqaM gRhasya pAːrzrveː vidyamAːnasya ninbavRkSasya zAːKAːnAːM maDyeː sTAːpitavAːn .
4_987 vaNik BoːjanAːdikaM samAːpya zayanam akaroːt .
4_988 tAːvatAː saH coːraH cOːryaM kartuM tadgRhasamI:pam Aːgatya bahiH AːtmAːnaM goːpayitvAː sTitavAːn .
4_989 kiYcit kAːla anantaraM vaNijaH patnI: ucca svareːNa taM - BoːH BavAːn DanaM sarvaM kutra sTAːpitavAːn asti .
4_990 ahaM tu BI:tAː asmi .
4_991 pratidinaM cOːryavAːrtAː zrUːyateː .
4_992 nagareː coːraBI:tiH aDikAː jAːtAː asti iti uktvatI: .
4_993 tadAː vaNik - priyeː ! mAːstu kiYcit api Bayam .
4_994 asmAːkaM DanaM surakSitam asti .
4_995 coːraH AːgacCati ceːt saH gRheː kimapi na prAːpnoːti .
4_996 yataH ahaM DanaM sarvaM Gaqeː saMsTAːpya taM GaqaM nimbavRkSasya upari sTAːpitavAːn .
4_997 gRhAːt bahiH sTitaH coːraH tayoːH samBAːSaNaM purNaM zrutavAːn .
4_998 saH manasi eːva cintitavAːn - eːSaH vaNik budDimAːn asti .
4_999 gRhAːt bahiH DaNa goːpitavAːn asti .
5_1201 BAːratasya svatantratAːsawgrAːmeː gAːnDimahoːdasya anuyAːyiSu rAːjeːndramahoːdayaH viziSqaH AːsI:t .
5_1202 saH niSVAːvAːn, utsAːhI: parizramI: ca svatantratAːsawgrAːmI: AːsI:t .
5_1203 eːkamnavadveːeːkam I:savI:yasya asahayoːgAːndoːlaneː eːkamnavacatvAːridveː I:savI:yasya BAːrataM muYca-Aːndoːlaneː anyeːSu svatantratAːndoːlaneːSu ca saH bahuvAːraM kAːrAːvAːsamapi asahat .
5_1204 eːkamnavacatvAːrisapta I:savI:yeː yadAː deːzaH svatantroː$Bavat tadAː rAːjeːndramahoːdayaH praTamaH KAːdyamantrI: aBavat .
5_1205 tataH saH deːzasya praTamarAːSqrapatipadaM cAːlawkRtavAːn .
5_1206 dveːaSqa ParavarI: eːkamnavaSaqtriNi dinAːwkeː tasya deːhAːvasAːnaBavat .
5_1207 rAːjeːndraprasAːdaH svaBAːveːna saralaH maDuraBAːSI: cAːsI:t .
5_1208 saH BAːratI:yasaMskRteːH prazaMsakaH saMvarDakazca AːsI:t .
5_1209 saralaM jI:vanaM uccaH vicAːraH ityeːtasya saH pratyakSaM udAːharaNamAːsI:t
5_1210 teːna AːjI:vanaM BAːratI:yaM vastraM DAːritam .
5_1211 satyaM saralatAː ca tasya jI:vanamantrOː AːstAːm .
5_1212 eːtasya mahAːpurUːSasya mahatI: deːzaseːvAː uttamaM ca caritraM sarvEːrasmAːBiH anukaraNI:yameːvAːsti .
5_1213 dineːzasya patram prAːptaM tava patram .
5_1214 kuzalamaM vijYAːya paraM prasI:dAːmi .
5_1215 atrAːpi sarvaM kuzalamasti .
5_1216 mitra ! tuByaM saMskRtaM kaTaM na roːcateː .
5_1217 BAːSAːsu saMskRtaM maDuraM, prAːcI:natamaM vEːBavamayaM ca .
5_1218 BAːratI:yAː saMskRtiH saMskRtam avalambateː .
