5_1220 mitra ! vizvasAːhityeː saMskRtasya gOːravamayaM sTAːnamasti .
5_1221 saMsAːrasya sarvazreːSVani aneːkAːni pustakAːni saMskRteː liKitAːni santi .
5_1222 veːdAːH, upaniSadaH, mahAːBAːratam, rAːmAːyaNam, gI:tAː, paYcatantram AːdayaH aneːkAːH granTAːH jagataH AːkarSaNasya keːndram .
5_1223 saMskRtam aDyAːtmavidyAːyAːH niDAːnam asti .
5_1224 aneːkeː vEːdeːzikAːH api AːtmajYAːnAːya idAːnI:M saMskRtaM zikSanteː .
5_1225 saMskRtaBAːSAː bahUːnAːM BAːratI:yaBAːSAːNAːM jananI: asti .
5_1226 kimaDikeːna, BAːratI:yAː rI:tiH, nI:tiH, AːcAːraH, vyavahAːraH, jYAːnaM vijYAːnaM ca sarvamatra mUːlarUːpeːNa vidyateː .
