5_1234 durgAːpUːjAːyAːH viSayeː aneːkAːH kaTAːH pracalitAːH santi .
5_1235 rAːvaNeːna saha yudDAːt pUːrvaM zrI:rAːmaH dazadinAːni yAːvat durgAːyAːH pUːjAːM kRtavAːn .
5_1236 tasyAːH prasAːdeːna saH rAːvaNaM hatavAːn lawkAːyAːM vijayaM prAːptavAːn ca .
