5_1322 BikSayAː saYciteːna Daneːna saH goːDUːmacUːrNaM krI:NAːti sma .
5_1323 saH atI:va kRpaNaH AːsI:t .
5_1324 ataH tat cUːrNam aBuktvAː eːkasmin mRdGaqeː saYcinoːti sma .
5_1325 eːSaH GaqaH tasya zayyAːyAːH pAːrzveː eːkasmin nAːgadanteː lambamAːnaH AːsI:t .
5_1326 eːkadAː saH zayyAːyAːM lambAːyamAːnaH acintayat-zI:Grameːva goːDUːmacUːrNeːna ahaM GaqaM pUːrayiSyAːmi .
5_1327 cUːrNapUːritaM GaqaM haqqaM neːSyAːmi .
