5_1334 dugDasya vikreːyeːNa yat Danam AːgamiSyati teːna eːkaM sundaraM BavanaM nirmAːsyAːmi .
5_1335 tataH vivAːhaM kariSyAːmi .
5_1336 suKeːna nivasiSyAːmi .
5_1337 BikSukaH agreː acintayat-kadAːcit mama BAːryAː svapitRgRhaM gantuM vadiSyati .
