5_1344 kAːlpanikasya suKasya mUːlameːva naSqam .
5_1345 eːvameːva nirUːdyamasya janasya keːvalaM kalpitaM suKaM duHKAːya eːva Bavati .
5_1346 udyameːna hi siDyanti kAːryAːNi na manoːraTEːH .
5_1347 gururbrahmAː gururviSNuH gururdeːvoː maheːzvaraH .
