5_1352 pAːtratvAːd Danam Aːpnoːti, DanAːd DarmaM tataH suKam .
5_1353 aBivAːdanzI:lasya nityaM vRdDoːpaseːvinaH .
5_1354 catvAːri tasya varDanteː AːyurvidyAː yazoː balam .
5_1355 apUːrvaH koː$pi koːzoː$yaM vidyateː tava BAːrati .
5_1356 vyayatoː vRdDimAːyati kSayamAːyati saYcayAːt .
5_1357 yasya budDirbalaM tasya.
5_1358 kasmiMscid vaneː BAːsurakaH nAːmaH siMhaH avasat .
5_1359 saH pratidinam aneːkeːSAːM pazUːnAːM vaDam akaroːt .
5_1360 eːkadAː vanasya sarveː pazavaH tasya siMhasya samI:pamagacCan avadat ca - mRgeːndra ! tvaM kimarTaM pazUːnAːM vaDaM karoːSi .
5_1361 yadi eːkeːnEːva tava tRptirBavati vayaM svayameːva tava BoːjanAːya pratidinam eːkaM pazuM preːSayiSyAːmaH .
5_1362 teːSAːM vacanAːni zrutvAː BAːsurakoː$vadat -yadi yUːyam eːvaM vadaTa tahi Bavatu taTAː .
5_1363 parantu yadi kasmiMscid divaseː mama BoːjanAːya eːkaH pazuH nAːgamiSyati tahi ahaM sarveːSAːM pazUːnAːM vaDaM kariSyAːmi .
