5_1365 eːkadAː eːkasya zazakasya vAːraH AːsI:t .
5_1366 saH acintayat - yadi mama maraNaM nizcitamasti tahi ahaM mandaM mandaM gacCAːmi .
5_1367 saH zazakaH mAːrgeː eːkaM kUːpamapazyat .
5_1368 tasmin kUːpeː svapratibimbaM dRSqvAː saH eːkam upAːyamacintayat .
