5_1370 kSuDAːpI:xitaH BAːsurakaH taM dRSqavAː krudDoː$Bavat apRcCat ca - kimarTaM tvaM vilambeːna Aːgatoː$si .
5_1371 prAːtaH ahamavaSyameːva sarveːSAːM pazUːnAːM vaDaM kariSyAːmi .
5_1372 zazakaH vinayeːna avadat -mRgarAːja ! atra aham anyeːSAːM ca pazUːnAːM doːSoː nAːsti .
5_1373 ahaM tu paYcazazakEːH saha tava samI:peː AːgantuM pravRtaH Aːsam .
5_1374 paraM mAːrgeː eːkaH aparaH siMhaH asmAːn amilat avadat ca -ahamasya vanasya nRpaH asmi .
5_1375 ataH ahaM yuSmAːn BakSayiSyAːmi .
5_1376 ahaM tamavadam - asya vanasya nRpastu BAːsurakaH nAːma siMhaH asti .
5_1377 saH adya asmAːn BakSayiSyati .
5_1378 eːtat zrutvAː saH siMhaH atikrudDoː$Bavat .
5_1379 ahaM tu punaH AːgamiSyAːmi iti zapaTaM kRtvAː atra Aːgatoː$smi .
5_1380 eːtadAːkarNya BAːsurakaH kroːDeːna avadat -saH aparaH siMhaH kutra vasati .
5_1381 taM zI:GraM mahyaM darzaya .
5_1382 tadAː saH zazakaH BAːsurakameːkasya kUːpasya samI:peː anayat akaTayat ca - asmin kUːpeː saH siMhaH vasati.
5_1383 BAːsurakaH tasmin kUːpeː svapratibimbaM dRSqvAː ayam aparaH siMhaH iti matvAː uccEːH agarjat .
5_1384 svazabdasya pratiDvaniM zrutvAː saH tasmin kUːpeː akUːrdat prAːNAːn ca atyajat .
