5_1395 grAːmeːSu kRSakAːH prAːtarAːzaM kRtvAː halasahitAːn balI:vardAːn nI:tvAː kSeːtrAːNi prati gacCanti .
5_1396 janAːH upavaneːSu BramaNaM kurvanti .
5_1397 CAːtrAːH vidyAːlayaM gacCanti .
5_1398 teː tatra pAːVAːn paVanti leːKAːn ca liKanti .
5_1399 asmAːkaM jI:vaneː sUːryasya atyaDikaM mahattvamasti .
5_1400 asyEːva prakAːzeː sarvaH vyavahAːraH pracalati .
5_1401 dinapati-ravi-dinamaNi-Aːditya-BAːskara-dineːza-ityAːdI:ni asya aneːkAːni aBiDAːnAːni santi.
5_1402 gAːyatrI:mantraH asyEːva stutiM karoːti .
5_1403 mahAːtmanaH gAːnDinaH janma eːkamaSqaSaqnava tameː varSeː aktUːbaramAːsasya dvitI:yAːyAːM tAːrikAːyAːm gujarAːtapradeːzeː poːrabandaranAːmni nagareː$Bavat .
5_1404 asya pituH nAːma karamacandagAːnDI: mAːtuH ca nAːma putalI:bAːI: AːsI:t .
