5_1407 eːkadAː tasya vidyAːlayeː eːkaH nirI:kSakaH AːgacCat .
5_1408 saH CAːtrAːn parI:kSituM kEːqala iti AːMglaBAːSAːyAːH zabdaM leːKitumAːdizat .
5_1409 moːhanadAːsaH taM zabdamazudDam aliKat .
5_1410 tadAː tasya adyAːpakaH anyasya samI:pasTasya CAːtrasya pustikAːM dRSqvAː tasya zabdasya varNavinyAːsam anukartuM taM saMkeːteːnAːkaTayat .
5_1411 paraM teːna eːtad nAːcaritam .
5_1412 yadAː sa uccazikSAːyEː iMglEːNxa-deːzamagacCat tadAː saH pratijYAːtrayamakaroːt - eːkam.
5_1413 ahaM kadAːpi madirAːM na seːviSyeː .
