5_1423 AːMglI:yAːH bahuvAːraM taM kAːrAːgAːreː akSipan .
5_1424 asya mahAːpuruSasya prayatnEːH BAːrataM svatantramaBavat .
5_1425 mahAːtmanAː gAːnDinAː DarmaviSayeː AːcAːraviSayeː ca bahu liKitam .
5_1426 paraM satyasya mama prayoːgaH iti zI:rSakeːNa AːtmakaTAː zrI:madaBagavadgI:tAːyAːzca anAːsaktinAːmakaM BAːSyam iti racanAːdvayaM mahattvapUːrNamasti .
5_1427 eːSaH mahAːpurUːSaH rAːStrapitAː itiBiDAːnamapi prAːptavAːn .
5_1428 eːkamnavacatvAːrisapta tameː varSeː janavarI:mAːsasya triMzattamyAːM tAːrikAːyAːM eːkasya GAːtakasya gulikayAː Aːhatoː BUːtvAː heː rAːma ityuccAːrayan saH svadeːham atyajat .
5_1429 trayoː DUːrtAːH kasmiMzcid nagareː mitrazarmAː nAːma eːkaH brAːhmaNaH avasat .
5_1430 saH eːkadAː eːkam ajaM skanDeː kRtvAː gRhaM pratyagacCat .
5_1431 tadAː trayoː DUːrtAːH mAːrgeː taM brAːhmaNam apazyan acintayan ca - eːtasmAːt brAːhmAːNAːt eːSaH ajaH asmAːBiH yeːna keːna upAːyeːna prAːptavyaH .
5_1432 aTa teːSu DUːrteːSu eːkaH DUːrtaH veːSaparivartanaM kRtvAː tasya brAːhamaNasya sammuKeː AːgacCat apRcCat ca - Boː brAːhamaNa ! tvam eːtaM kukkuraM kimarTaM vahasi .
5_1433 tasya vacan zrutvAː mitrazarmAː avadat - eːSaH kukkuraH na asti .
5_1434 eːSaH tu ajaHasti .
5_1435 aTa kiYcid dUːraM gatvAː taM brAːhamaNaM dvitI:yaH DUːrtaH amilat aBaNat ca - Boː brAːhamaNa ! tvaM kimarTam eːtam apavitraM kukkuraM skanDeː kRtvAː nayasi .
5_1436 tadAː saH brAːhmaNaH krudDoː$Bavat akaTayat ca - heː murKa ! kiM tvaM anDaH asi yad ajaM kukkuram avagacCasi .
5_1437 aTa kiYcid dUːraM gatvAː tRtI:yaH DUːrtaH taM brAːhamaNaM amilat taTEːva ca avadat .
