5_1448 durjanaH parihartavyoː vidyayAː$lawkRtoː$pi san .
5_1449 maNinAː BUːSitaH sarpaH kimasOː na BayawkaraH .
5_1450 BAːratavarSasya uttaradizAːyAːM himAːlayoː nAːma parvatoː$sti .
5_1451 asya parvatasya ziKarAːNi atyunntAːni santi .
5_1452 eːtAːni ziKarAːNi sadEːva himeːna AːcCAːditAːni santi .
5_1453 ata eːva asya parvatasya aBiDAːnaM himasya AːlayaH himAːlaya iti prasidDoː$sti .
5_1454 himAːlayAːt gaMgAː-yamunAː-zatadru-vipAːzAː-irAːvatI:-vitastAː-praBRtayaH aneːkAːH nadyaH prAːdurBavanti .
5_1455 eːtAːsAːM nadI:nAːM jalaM BAːratavarSasya vizAːlaM BUːBAːgaM siYcati .
5_1456 ata eːva asmin deːzeː praBUːtAːni viviDAːni annAːni PalAːni ca udBavanti .
5_1457 asmin parvateː viviDAːH oːSaDayaH vRkSAːH DAːtavaH viviDAːni ca ratnAːni upalaByanteː .
5_1458 grI:SmakAːleː tAːpeːna vyAːkulAːH janAːH himAːlayasya parvatI:yasTaleːSu gacCanti suKaM ca anuBavanti .
5_1459 asmin eːva parvateː mAːnasaroːvara-amaranAːTa-badrI:nAːTa-keːdAːranAːTa-haridvAːra-praBRtI:ni aneːkAːni darzanI:yAːni tI:rTasTAːnAːni aneːkeː ca deːvAːlayaH santi .
5_1460 eːtasmin parvateː sTitAːsu aneːkAːsu guhAːsu sAːDakAːH tapazcaranti .
5_1461 atra deːvI:nAːM mandirAːNi api santi .
5_1462 eːtasmAːt kAːraNAːt ayaM parvatoː deːvaBUːmirAːpi kaTyateː .
5_1463 himeːna AːcCAːditAːni asya unnatAːni ziKarAːNi atizEːtyAːt zatruByazca asmAːn rakSanti .
5_1464 ayaM parvataH surakSAː-dRSqayAː atI:va mahatvapUːrNoː$sti .
5_1465 aneːnEːva kAːraNeːna asmAːkaM surakSAː-sEːnikAːH asya rakSAːyEː tatparAːH Bavanti .
5_1466 matsyatraya -kaTAː.
5_1467 kasmiMzcit jalAːzayeː anAːgataviDAːtAː, pratyupannamatiH yadBaviSyazceːti trayaH matsyAːH avasan .
5_1468 kadAːcit taM jalAːzayam avaloːkya DI:varAːH parasparam avadan - asmin jalAːzayeː bahavaH matsyAːH
5_1469 eːtAːdRzaM nizcayaM kRtvAː teː agacCan .
5_1470 tadanantaraM teːSAːM vacanaM zrutvAː teːSu matsyeːSu anAːgataviDAːtAː nAːma matsyaH akaTayat - zvaH praBAːtasamayeː teː DI:varAːH atra AːgamiSyanti sarvAːn ca matsyAːn jAːleː badDvAː neːSyanti .
5_1471 eːtat AːkarNya pratyutpannamatiH nAːma matsyaH avadat - tvayAː samyag Aːloːcitam .
5_1472 tasya vacanaM zrutvAː yadBaviSyaH nAːma matsyaH uccEːH vihasya akaTayat - n samyageːtat yataH teːSAːM DI:varAːNAːM kaTanamAːtreːNa eːtasmAːt jalAːzayAːt anyatra gantumicCataH .
5_1473 ahaM tu atra eːva sTAːsyAːmi .
5_1474 aTa yadBaviSyasya nizcayaM jYAːtvAː anAːgatyaviDAːtAː pratyupannamatiH ca anyatra agacCatAːm .
5_1475 anAːgataviDAːtAː ca pratutpannamatistaTAː .
5_1476 dvAːveːtOː suKameːDeːteː yadBaviSyoː vinaSyati .
5_1477 ayam utsavaH agastamAːsasya paYcadazyAːM tiTOː Bavati .
5_1478 pUːrvaM BAːratadeːzaH parAːDI:naH AːsI:t .
5_1479 asmin eːva divaseː eːkamnavacatvAːrisapta tameː varSeː asmAːkaM deːzaH svatantroː$Bavat .
5_1480 ataH eːva BAːratI:yAːH prativarSam eːtasminneːva divaseː imam utsavaM samAːyoːjayanti .
5_1481 loːkamAːnyaH bAːlagaMgAːDaratilakaH, mahAːtmAː gAːnDI:, javAːharalAːlaH neːharUːH eːteː anyeː ca aneːkeː mahAːpuruSAːH BAːratadeːzasya svatantratAːyEː mahAːntaM prayatnam akurvan .
5_1482 BAːratasya svatantratAːyAːH kRteː BagatasiMhasuKadeːvaAːdayaH aneːkeː deːzaBaktAːH svaprAːNAːn atyajan .
5_1483 dillI:nagareː eːtasya utsavasya zoːBAː atI:va ramaNI:yAː Bavati .
5_1484 eːtasmin divaseː prAːtaH raktadurgasya prAːkAːreː asmAːkaM deːzasya praDAːnamantrI: DvajAːroːhaNaM karoːti .
5_1485 DvajAːroːhaNAːnantaraM praDAːnamantrI: deːzaM prati sandizati .
5_1486 gRheːSu sTitAːH janAːH api imaM kAːryakramaM dUːradarzaneː avaloːkayanti .
5_1487 rAːtrOː vidyuddI:pakEːH sarvAːNi rAːSqriyaBavanAːni zoːBanteː .
