6_1633 aByAːseːna mAːnavaH kimapi sAːDayituM zaknoːti iti.
6_1634 bAːlikAːyAːH vacanaM zrutvAː mahAːrAːjaH nitarAːM krudDaH aBavat.
6_1635 saH AːjYAːM kRRtavAːna yat -eːSAː bAːlikAː rAːjyAːt niSkAːsanI:yAː iti.
6_1636 pAːlaH eːteːna nitarAːM du:KitaH aBavat .
6_1637 parantu sAː bAːlikAː pitaraM santoːSayantI: uktavatI:- tAːta! eːSa: mUːXaH mahAːrAːjaH adya mama vacanaM na awgI:karoːti .
6_1638 mAː astu cintAː.
6_1639 ahaM pratijYAːM karoːmi yat eːkadAː svakI:yeːna aByAːsabaleːna asmin eːva kSeːtreː mahat balapradarzanaM kRtvAː mahAːrAːjam AːzcaryacakitaM kariSyAːmi iti.
6_1640 sAː tataH miTilAːnagaraM parityajya pAːqaliputraM gatavatI: .
6_1641 tatra nagarAːt bahi: eːkaM laGukuqI:raM nirmAːya BikSAːvRttyAː jI:vanaM karoːti.
6_1642 kAːlAːntareː sAː BikSayAː prAːpteːna Daneːna eːkAːM mahiSI:M krI:tvAː AːnI:tavatI: .
6_1643 tasyEː pratidinaM tRNa Aːdikam AːhAːraM dadAːti .
6_1644 sAːyawkAːleː dugDadoːhanaM kRtvAː nagareː vikrayaNaM karoːti.
6_1645 teːna eːva jI:vanayAːpanaM ca karoːti.
6_1646 gacCatAː kAːleːna sAː mahiSI: putraM eːkam ajanayat.
6_1647 tata: AːraBya sAː bAːlikAː pratidinamapi taM bAːlamahiSaM skanDeː niDAːya DAːvanasya aByAːsaM karoːti.
6_1648 varSatrayAːnantaraM saH vizAːlakAːyaH mahiSa: aBavat.
6_1649 idAːnI:m api bAːlikAː vinAː AːyAːsaM taM skanDeː niDAːya DAːvati.
6_1650 punaH kadAːcit sAː mahiSam AːdAːya miTilAːnagaram AːgatavatI: tasmin avasareː eːva tatra prativarSam iva vI:ratAːpradarzanam Aːyoːjitam AːsI:t.
6_1651 bAːlikAː kaTam api tatra svI:yabalapradarzanAːya anumatiM prAːptavati upasTiteː janasamUːheː upasTiteː ca rAːjaparivAːreː bAːlikAː agreː Aːgatya Jaqiti taM mahAːmahiSam utTAːpya skaMDeː niDAːya tat kSeːtraM paritaH paYcavAːraM DAːvitavatI: .
6_1652 taTAː api tasya muKeː zrAːnteːH cinham api na dRSqam .
6_1653 eːtad dRSqvAː nitarAːM vismRtaH mahAːrAːjaH harisiMhadeːvaH AːsanAːt utTAːya uktavAːn ahoː Aːzcaryam ati AːzcaryaM pradarzanam idam.
6_1654 adyAːvaDi mayAː idRzaM pradarzanaM kadAːpi nEːva dRSqam .
6_1655 ataH nizcitarupeːNa api iyaM bAːlikAː sammAːnanI:yAː iti.
6_1656 tataH saH samamahiSaBAːreːNa Daneːna tasyAːH bAːlikAːyAːH sammAːnam akaroːt.
6_1657 bAːlikAː api svapratijYAːpUːrtyAː santuSqAː aBavat.
6_1658 sa kAːrpAːsasya vikreːtAː AːsI:t .
6_1659 kAːrpAːsasya vyavasAːyeːnEːva teːna vipulaM DanaM saMgRhI:tam .
6_1660 paraM sa prakRtyAː atyantaM kRpaNa AːsI:t .
6_1661 alpasyAːpi Danasya vyayaH taM BRzamapI:xayat.
6_1662 DanarAːjaH ,DanaganDaH,DanaprI:tiH,Danarucizca iti teːSAːM nAːmAːni Aːsan .
6_1663 zEːzaveː eːva DanapAːleːna teː Danasya mahattvaM vAːraM vAːraM pAːVitAːH .
6_1664 itTaM teː$pi pitRvat kRpaNAːH saYjAːtAːH.
6_1665 yadAː DanapAːlaH paYcatattvaM gataH tadAː tasya putrAːH parasparaM vaYcayantaH yAːvatCakyaM DanaM grahI:tuM prAːyatanta .
6_1666 kiMtu sarveː$pi putrAː DanaprAːptOː jAːgarUːkAː Aːsan .
6_1667 ataH teː anyoː$nyaM vaYcayituM nAːzaknuvan .
6_1668 tatasteː nirNI:tavantaH, pituH DanaM caturSu samaBAːgeːSu viBAːjyam, eːkEːkazca BAːgaH eːkEːkasmEː BAːtreː deːya iti .
6_1669 tadanantaraM DanarAːzeːH catvAːraH samAː BAːgAːH kRtAːH .
6_1670 kalahaM vinAː eːkEːkazca BAːgaH tEːH svI:kRtaH .
6_1671 yadAː teː pituH vastUːNAːM saMcayasya BAːgAːn kartum AːraBanta tadAː dvayoːH vastunoːH viSayeː mahAːn kalahaH aBavat .
6_1672 teː ca vastunI: AːstAːM pituH gRhaM gRhapAːlazca .
6_1673 sarveː BAːtaroː gRhaM hastayituM prAːyatanta .
6_1674 koː$pi BAːtAː gRhapAːlasya pAːlanAːya poːSaNAːya cAːlpasya api Danasya vyayaM kartuM nEːcCat .
6_1675 bahoːH kAːlAːd anantaraM kalahaH azAːmyat .
6_1676 gRhasya samAːn BAːgAːn kRtvAː catvAːroː BrAːtaraH tatra pRTag pRTak avasan .
6_1677 gRhapAːlasya ca viSayeː teː nirNI:tavantaH , asya gRhapAːlasya praTamaH pAːdaH DanarAːjasya, dvitI:yaH pAːdoː DanaganDasya, tRtI:yaH pAːdaH DanaprI:teːH,caturTazca pAːdaH DanaruceːH asti .
6_1678 asya pAːlanAːya poːSaNAːya ca yoːvyayoː Baveːt soː$smAːBiH sarvEːH kAːryaH .
6_1679 kadAːcit sa gRhapAːlaH DanaganDasya gRhaBAːgeː gatvAː dugDam apibat .
6_1680 saH eːtad apazyat .
6_1681 krudDoː BUːtvAː DanaganDoː daNxeːna gRhapAːlaM prAːharat .
6_1682 teːna gRhapAːlasya caturTaH pAːdaH kSataH .
6_1683 ataH tasya pAːdasya rakSakeːNa DanaruciNAː tEːlAːrdreːNa kAːrpAːseːna pUːrNam vastraKaNxaM kSateː pAːdeː badDam .
6_1684 akasmAːt tasmAːt agneːH sPuliwgAː utpatitAːH tEːH sPuliwgEːH gRhapAːlasya kSateː pAːdeː badDaM vastraKaNxaM jvalayitum AːraBata .
6_1685 gRhapAːloː BI:taH san itastataH aDAːvat .
6_1686 yAːvad agniH sarveːSu gRhaBAːgeːSu prAːrasat tAːvaccatvAːroː BrAːtaroː yAːvad gRhI:tuM zakyaM tAːvad gRhI:tvAː gRhAːd nirgatAːH .
6_1687 zI:Grameːva sarvaM gRham adahat .
6_1688 krudDAːsteː eːSa tavAːparAːDoː$sti eːSa tavAːparAːDoː$sti iti kaTayantaH kalaham akurvan .
6_1689 tataH DanaruciH triBiH BrAːtRBiH badDaH .
6_1690 trayoː BrAːtaraH DanaruciM badDvAː nyAːyAːlayaM anayan .
6_1691 tAːn dRSqvAː nyAːyAːDI:zoː$vadat-yUːyaM sarveː aBiyoːktAːraH sTa eːSa ca badDaH puruSoː$Biyukta iti pratiBAːti .
6_1692 keː yUːyam eːSa badDaH puruSoː$mAːkaM kaniSVoː BrAːtAː asti .
6_1693 gRhadAːhasya eːSa eːva karaNam .
6_1694 ata eːva daNxamahati .
6_1695 nyAːyAːDI:zoː$vadat-heː aBiyoːktAːraH ! aham aparAːDam ajYAːtvAː ,aparAːDasya pramAːNam alabDvAː ,aBiyuktasya aBiyoːktRNAːM ca yuktI:H azrutvAː na kamapi daNxayAːmi .
6_1696 kaTayata,ka eːtasya aBiyuktAːsyAːparAːDaH .
6_1697 tadAː DanaganDoː$vadat-eːSaH gRhamadahat.
6_1698 nyAːyAːDI:zaH apRcCat-kaTam.
6_1699 aparAːDasya kiM pramAːNam .
6_1700 kAː vAː yuSmAːkaM yuktiH .
6_1701 tasya praTamasya pAːdasya rakSakaH jyeːSVoː BrAːtAː, dvitI:yasya pAːdasya DanaganDaH, tRtI:yasya pAːdasya ahaM caturTasya ca pAːdasya eːSa DanaruciH akSakoː nirDAːritaH .
6_1702 yadAː gRhapAːlasya caturTeː pAːdeː kSatam aBavat tadAː aneːna tEːlAːrdreːNa kAːrpAːseːna pUːrNaM vastraKaNxaM tasya caturTeː pAːdeː badDam .
6_1703 tadanantaraM vastraKaNxaM ajvalayat .
6_1704 BI:taH san gRhapAːlaH itastataH aDAːvat sarvaM gRhaM adahat .
6_1705 ataH gRhapAːlasya caturTaH pAːdoː gRhadAːhasya kAːraNam .
6_1706 tasya pAːdasya rakSakaH eːSaH kaniSVaH BrAːtAː gRhadAːhasya karttAː asti .
6_1707 ataeːva eːSa daNxanI:yaH .
6_1708 eːteːna asmAːkaM hAːniH pUːraNI:yAː.
6_1709 nyAːyAːDI:zoː$BiyuktamapRcCat-kimeːtat satyam .
6_1710 kaniSVoː BrAːtAː avadat-mAːnanI:ya !ahaM caturTasya pAːdasya rakSakoː$smi iti satyam .
6_1711 tasmin pAːdeː tEːlAːrdreːNa kAːrpAːseːna pUːrNaM vastraKaNxaM mayAː badDaM iti satyam .
6_1712 vastraKaNxam ajvalad ityapi satyam .
6_1713 kintu ahaM gRhadAːhasya kartAː nAːsmi .
6_1714 vastutaH eːteː sarveː aBiyuktAːH santi .
6_1715 eːtEːH mama hAːniH pUːraNI:yAː.
6_1716 DanaruciH abravI:t-gRhadAːhasya sAːkSAːt kAːraNaM kiM vartateː .
6_1717 gRhapAːlaH itastataH aDAːvat .
6_1718 tasmAːt agniH gRhasya sarveːSu BAːgeːSu prAːrasat .
6_1719 kiM gRhapAːlaH teːna pAːdeːna aDAːvat yasmin pAːdeː tEːlAːrdreːNa kAːrpAːseːna yuktaM vastraKaNxaM badDam.
6_1720 na tat saMBavati iti spaSqameːva .
6_1721 gRhapAːlaH anyEːH triBiH pAːdEːH agniM sarveːSu gRhaBAːgeːSu prasAːrayitum azaknoːt yeːSAːM rakSakAːH mama BrAːtaraH santi .
6_1722 atasteː eːva gRhadAːhasya kartAːraH .
6_1723 tEːreːva mama hAːniH pUːraNI:yAː .
6_1724 tatoː nyAːyAːDI:zeːna upagataH .
6_1725 ataH saH banDanAːd moːcitaH .
6_1726 nyAːyAːDI:zeːna trayoːH BrAːtaraH AːjYAːpitAːH-pUːrayata DanaruceːH hAːnim.
6_1727 ataH tat cUːrNam aBuktvAː eːkasmin mRdGaqeː saYcinoːti sm .
6_1728 mRdGaqaH BagnaH goːDUːmacUːrNaM ca BUːmOː vikSiptam .
6_1729 udyAːneːSu zAːlI:mAːra-nizAːta iti dveː udyAːneː prasidDeː manoːrameː ca staH .
6_1730 atra janAːH zikAːrAː iti nOːkayAː jalavihAːraM kurvanti prasannAːH ca Bavanti .
6_1731 eːSa Kalu duSqamahoːragakulAːvAːsaH.
6_1732 pazyantu BavatyaH.
6_1733 vRdDagoːpAːlakaH - hAː BartaH! eːSa kanyakAːBiH vAːryamAːNoː yamunAːhradaM praviSqaH .
6_1734 mAː Kalu mAː Kalu sAːhasaM kRtvAː praveːSqum .
6_1735 atra vyAːGrAː varAːhAː hastinaH pAːnI:yaM pI:tvAː tatrEːva mriyanteː .
6_1736 kaTaM na dRzyateː.
6_1737 kimidAːnI:M karoːmi.
6_1738 Bavatu, imaM tAːvat kumBapalAːzamAːrUːhya niDyAːyAːmi.
6_1739 hAː hAː DUːma utTitaH.
6_1740 saMkarSaNaH pazyantu BavatyaH
6_1741 vRdDagoːpAːlakaH- hI: hI: sAːDu BartaH! sAːDu!.
6_1742 kAːliyasya paYca PaNAːn
6_1743 dAːmoːdaraH-kAːliya! kimarTamidAːnI:M yamunAːhRdaM
6_1744 kAːliyaH -prasI:datu Bagavan ! ajYAːnAːd atikrAːntavAːn , sAːntaHpuraH zaraNAːgatoː$smi.
6_1745 tadicCAːmi garuwAːdaBayaM BagavatprasAːdAːt.
6_1746 dAːmoːdaraH -aneːna baleːna BavAːn garvitaH.
6_1747 dAːmoːdaraH - pravizatu BavAːn.
6_1748 tadidAːnI:meːva viSaM saMhratya yamunAːhradAːd niSkrAːmAːmi.
6_1749 satyameːva jayateː BAːratasya AːdarzavAːkyam asti .
6_1750 asya rAːSqriyaH DvajaH trirawgam asti .
6_1751 janagaNamana eːtasya rAːSqragAːnam vandeː mAːtaram rAːSqragI:tam ca asti .
6_1752 BAːratasya rAːjaDAːnI: dillI: asti .
6_1753 dI:pAːvalI: BAːratavarSasya eːkaH mahAːn utsavaH astti .
6_1754 ayam utsavaH kAːrtika-mAːsAːsya amAːvasyAːyAːm Bavati .
6_1755 idam kaTyateː yat rAːvaNam hatvAː rAːmaH asmin eːva divaseː sI:tayAː lakSmaNeːna ca saha ayoːDyAːm prati AːgacCat .
6_1756 tadAː ayoːDyAːyAːH janAːH atI:va prasannAːH aBavan .
6_1757 ataH teː svAːni gRhAːNi dI:pAːnAːm mAːlAːBiH Aːloːkayan .
6_1758 tataH praBRti prativarSam tasmin eːva divaseː eːSaH utsavaH Bavati .
6_1759 sarveː janAːH svagRhAːNi svacCAːni kurvanti, suDayAː limpanti sundarEːH ca citrEːH BUːSayanti .
6_1760 teː sva-mitreːByaH banDuByaH ca miSqAːnnam preːSayanti .
6_1761 bAːlakAːH bAːlikAːH ca krI:xanakAːnAːm miSqAːnnAːnAːm sPoːqaka-padAːrTAːnAːm ca krayaNam kurvanti .
6_1762 sAːyaMkAːleː sarveː janAːH dI:pAːnAː mAːlAːH prajjvAːlayanti .
6_1763 dI:pAːnAːm prakAːzaH anDakAːram apanayati .
6_1764 puruSAːH striyaH bAːlakAːH bAːlikAːH ca nUːtanAːni vastrAːNi DAːrayanti AːpaNAːnAːm ca zoːBAːm draSqum gacCanti .
6_1765 rAːtrOː janAːH lakSmI:m pUːjayanti miSqAːnnAːni ca BakSayanti .
6_1766 BAːratI:yAːH imam utsavam prativarSam soːllAːsam samAːyoːjayanti .
6_1767 gawgAː parvatarAːjahimAːlayAːt praBavati .
6_1768 eːSAː sarvAːsu nadI:Su zreːSVAː pavitratamAː ca asti .
6_1769 gawgAːyAːH udBavaviSayeː eːkAː kaTAː asti .
6_1770 BagI:raTaH nAːma nRpaH pUːrvajAːnAːm udDAːrAːya tapasyAːm akaroːt tapasyAːyAːH ca praBAːveːNa saH gawgAːM svargAːt DarAːyAːm avatAːrayituM samarTaH aBavat .
6_1771 ataH eːva imAːM janAːH BAːgI:raTI: iti api kaTayanti .
6_1772 teː asyAːH jalam atyaDikaM pAːvanaM manyanteː .
6_1773 bahavaH zradDAːlujanAːH pratidinam asyAːM snAːnaM kurvanti imAːM ca pUːjayanti .
6_1774 asyAːH taqeː haridvAːra-RSikeːSa-prayAːga-vAːrAːNasI:-ityAːdI:ni aneːkAːni tI:rTasTAːnAːni santi .
6_1775 prativarSaM puNyeːSu parvasu lakSAːNi janAːH eːSu tI:rTasTAːneːSu Aːgatya asyAːH pAːvanajaleːna snAːnaM kRtvAː duritAːni dUːrI:kurvanti .
6_1776 yantrakAːrAːH asyAːH jalamavarudDya seːtuM badDvAː mahAːjalAːSayeːSu jalasaYcayaM kurvanti .
6_1777 eːvaM prakAːreːNa saYcitaM jalaM kSeːtrAːNAːM siYcanAːya upayujyateː .
6_1778 aneːna BUːmiH urvarAː Bavati praBUːtaM ca annam utpAːdayati .
6_1779 eːvaM gawgAːyAːH jalaM kRSeːH mahAːntam upakAːraM karoːti .
6_1780 asyAːH jaleːna vidyut api utpannAː Bavati .
6_1781 iyaM dUːradarzana-DvanivikSeːpaka-zI:takEːtyAːdI:ni yantrAːNi saYcAːlayati viviDAːnAːM ca paNyAːnAːM vastUːnAːM nirmAːNeː sahAːyikAː Bavati .
6_1782 eːvaM gawgAː loːkaM paraloːkaM ca uBayam api upakaroːti .
6_1783 gRDramAːrjAːra kaTAː asyAːH krI:xAːyAːH vartamAːnaM svarUːpaM eːkamaSqaSaqtriNi tameː varSeː nizcitam aBUːt .
6_1784 uBayoːH pakSayoːH pratyeːkaM pakSeː eːkAːdaza krI:xakAːH BavantI:tyeːtat tu eːkamaSqasaptazUːnyam tameː varSeː nirDAːritam aBavat .
6_1785 eːtatsambanDinI: antAːrAːSqriyasaMsTAː eːkamnavazUːnyamcatvAːri tameː varSeː pratiSVAːpitAː .
6_1786 adyatveː eːSAː krI:xAː vizveː atyantam loːkapriyAː vartateː .
6_1787 pAːdakandukakrI:xAːyAːH vizvapratiyoːgitAː eːkamnavatriNizUːnyam tameː varSeː prAːrabDAː .
6_1788 eːkamnavaaSqaaSqa tamasya varSasya jUːna julAːI:mAːsayoːH PrAːMsadeːzasya rAːjaDAːnyAːM pEːrisanagareː pAːdakandukakrI:xAːyAːH yAː vizva pratiyoːgitAː aBavat tasyAːH saMkSiptaM vivaraNam atra prastUːyateː .
6_1789 teːSu deːzeːSu jarmanI: -iqalI: -arjeːnqI:nAː- xeːnamAːrka -ityeːtAːn deːzAːn kramazaH parAːjitya kroːziyAː -PrAːMsa -hAːlEːNxa -brAːjI:la ityeːteː catvAːroː deːzAːH vizvapratiyoːgitAːyAː upAːntimacaraNeː praviSqAː aBavan .
6_1790 dvitI:yAː sparDAː brAːjI:la-hAːlEːNxa deːzayoːH maDyeː aBavat .
6_1791 praTamAːyAːM sparDAːyAːM kroːziyAː- deːzasya - xeːvara- sUːkAː- nAːmakeːna krI:xakeːna pUːrvam eːkaM goːlaM kRtam .
6_1792 eːtadanantaraM kroːziyAː deːzasya daleːna AːtmarakSAːyEː mahAːn prayatnaH kRtAːH .
6_1793 asmin prayatneː kroːziyAː deːzasya krI:xakAːH PrAːMsadeːzI:yAːn krI:xakAːn vAːrayituM maDyAːntaraM yAːvat saPalAː aBavan dvitI:yeː kAːlAːrDeː liliyana-Turam-nAːmakeːna PrAːMsa-deːzasya krI:xakeːna goːlAːdvayaM kRtam.
6_1794 eːvaM PrAːMdeːzI:yakrI:xAːdaleːna kroːziyAːdeːzasya krI:xAːdalaM parAːjitam.
6_1795 dvitI:yAːyAːM sparDAːyAːM brAːjI:la -hAːlEːNxa- deːzOː nirDAːritasamayeː eːkEːkaM goːlaM kRtvAː tulyOː AːstAːm .
6_1796 hAːlEːNda- krI:xAːdalataH pEːqrika-klUːvaranAːmakeːna krI:xakeːna brAːjI:la deːzasya ca roːnEːlxoː nAːmakeːna prasidDeːna krI:xakeːna eːkEːkaM goːlaM kRtam.
6_1797 atirikta-samayeː$pi uBayoːH koː$pi pakSoː na parAːjitaH .
6_1798 pEːnalqI: -pAːdAːGAːteːSu brAːjI:la-deːzI:yeːna krI:xAːdaleːna hAːlEːNxadeːzasya krI:xAːdalaM parAːjitam .
6_1799 pratiyoːgitAːyAːH antimacaraNeː PrAːMsa- brAːjI:ladeːzayoːH maDyeː sparDAː aBavat .
6_1800 sparDAːyAːH prAːgeːva brAːjI:ladeːzasya prasidDaH roːnEːlxoːnAːmAː krI:xakaH AːkarSeːNa AːkrAːntoː$Bavat .
7_1801 asya eːkasmin pAːdeː pI:xAː$pi AːsI:t .
7_1802 parameːtasyAːmapi avasTAːyAːM brAːjI:ladeːzasya krI:xAːdalasya neːtAː taM svakI:yeː daleː viDRtavAːn .
7_1803 eːSa nirNayaH yuktoː nAːsI:t .
7_1804 asvasTatAːyAːH heːtoːH roːnEːlxoː sparDAːsamayeː krI:xAːkSeːtrAːt gamanAːgamanamakaroːt .
7_1805 goːlakaraNasya ca svarNAːvasaramapi prAːpya goːlaM kartuM nAːzaknoːt .
7_1806 eːteːna brAːjI:ladeːzasya krI:xakAːnAːm eːkAːgratAː BagnAː saMjAːtAː AːtmavizvAːsazca vyanazyat .
7_1807 PrAːMsadeːzasya krI:xakAːH eːtAːdRzI:M sTitiM vI:kSya DyAːneːna kOːzaleːna ca brAːjI:ladeːzasya krI:xAːdalasya aBiBavituM samarTAː aBavan .
7_1808 PrAːMsadeːzI:yadalasya neːtAː jiMdeːnamahoːdayaH zirasAː goːladvayaM kRtavAːn .
7_1809 avaziSqeːSu kSaNeːSu imEːnuala -pEːqiqa-nAːmakeːna krI:xakeːna kuzalatayAː tRtI:yamapi goːlaM kRtam .
7_1810 PrAːMsadeːzeːna trI:Ni goːlAːni kRtAːni .
7_1811 brAːjI:ladeːzasya upalabDistu zUːnyAː AːsI:t .
7_1812 eːvaM pUːrva vijeːtAːraM brAːjI:ladeːzaM parAːjitya PrAːMsadeːzaH pAːdakandukavizvapratiyoːgitAːyAːM vijeːtAː aBavat .
7_1813 dvOː unmattOː AːmravRkSam Aːruhya tasya zAːKAːyAːM lambamAːnOː AːstAːm .
7_1814 kiYcit kAːla anantaraM tayoːH anyataraH aDaH nyapatat .
7_1815 tadAː aparaH tam apRcCat-.
7_1816 kiM BavAːn zrAːntaH jAːtaH.
7_1817 na hi BrAːtaH! pakvaH jAːtaH .
7_1818 aparaH uttaram uktavAːn .
7_1819 aDyAːpakaH - saptAːhaH vyatI:taH ,tvaM vidyAːlayaM na AːgataH.
7_1820 CAːtra:- zrI:man ! mama svAːsTyaM samyak na AːsI:t .
7_1821 aDyAːpakaH - astu .
7_1822 kintu zvaH cikitsakAːt pramAːNapatram Aːnayatu.
7_1823 CAːtraH- zrI:man! BavAːn tasya sTAːneː paYca rupyakAːNi arTadaNxam eːva svI:karoːtu.
7_1824 cikitsakaH tu vEːdyakI:yapramAːNapatrasya kRteː paYcAːzat rupyakAːNi gRhNAːti.
7_1825 rameːzaH-BoːH vayasya! vadatu, vivAːha-avasareː varaHkimarTam azvasya upari upavizati,gardaBasya upari na.
7_1826 sureːzaH-BoːH mitra! BavAːn na jAːnAːti yat varaH yadi gardaBasya upari upavizati tarhi vaDUːH gardaBadvayaM dRSqvAː Bayam anuBUːya palAːyanaM karoːti.
7_1827 latAː- saKi! BavatI: jAːnAːti kiM sI:tAː rAːmeːNa saha kimarTaM vanaM gatavatI:.
7_1828 zAːntAː -Aːm, yataH sAː pativratAː.
7_1829 patiseːvAːyEː sahaDarmanirvAːhAːya sAː gatavatI:.
7_1830 kAːraNaM tu anyat asti.
7_1831 cintayatu, idAːnI:m eːkAː eːva zvazruH Bavati ceːt api jI:vanaM duSkaraM Bavati, tasyAːH tu tisraH zvazrava: Aːsan! kAː sTitiH syAːt tasyAːH!!.
7_1832 patiH patnI: tayoːH putraH ca vAːrtAːlAːpaM kurvantaH Aːsan.
7_1833 putraH pitaram apRcCat- pitaH! BavataH jI:vaneː atI:va ramaNI:yAːH divasAːH keː.
7_1834 pitAː- praTamaH divasaH saH yadAː ahaM sarvakAːrI:yaseːvAːM prAːptavAːn.
7_1835 dvitI:ya: divasaH yadAː BavAːn janma prAːptavAːn.
7_1836 mAːtAː maDyeː uktavatI:.
7_1837 kintu AːvayoːH vivAːhadivasaH.
7_1838 pitAː Jaqiti avadat.
7_1839 ahaM tu jI:vanasya suKapUːrNAːn ramaNI:yadivasAːn eːva vadan asmi idAːnI:m.
7_1840 nyAːyAːDI:zaH- tvayAː kaTaM cOːryaM kRtaM.
7_1841 coːraH nyAːyAːDI:zamahAːzaya ! BavAːn tat zikSitvAː kiM kariSyati.
7_1842 asya vAːtAːyanasya kAːcakaH keːna BagnaH.
7_1843 mI:rAː- mama patyAː.
7_1844 gOːrI:- tat kaTam.
7_1845 mI:rAː-mayAː taM prati caSakaH kSiptaH.
7_1846 kintu saH kiYcit apasRtavAːn .
7_1847 ataH caSakaH kAːcaka upari patitaH.
7_1848 kazcit rugNaH svasya udarasya zastrakriyAːrTaM nirdiSqeː dineː yaTAːsamayaM cikitsAːlayaM samprAːptaH.
7_1849 zalyaprakoːSVeː praveːzAːt prAːk saH svasya koːSeː sTitaM DanaM niSkAːsya gaNayitum AːrabDavAːn .
7_1850 eːtat dRzyaM pazyantI: zuBravastraDAːriNI: kAːpi paricAːrikAː tam avadat -zulkapradAːnasya cintAːM samprati mAː karoːtu .
7_1851 zastrakriyAːyAːH pazcAːt deːyapatrAːnusAːraM vayaM zulkaM svI:kurmaH.
7_1852 tadAː rugNaH avadat- BoːH mahoːdayeː! na meː cintAː yaTAː BavatI: vadati.
7_1853 zastrakriyAːrTaM saMmoːhanavAːyudAːnAːt prAːk ahaM sakRta DanaM gaNayitum icCAːmi.
7_1854 vijaya:-zrI:man! roːqikAː-capeːqikayoːH kaH BeːdaH .
7_1855 suDI:SqaH- kimarTaM vyarTameːva budDivyayaM karoːti BavAːn.
7_1856 sakRt dvayam api KAːditvAː pazyatu , svayam eːva BeːdaM jAːnAːti.
7_1857 vadatu, idAːnim eːva dadAːni kim.
7_1858 patiH prAːNavallaBeː! ahaM tu vivAːhAːt pUːrvaM atI:va duSqaH Aːsam.
7_1859 kintu BavatI: vadatu ,kaTam AːsI:t.
7_1860 patnI:-lajjayAː priya! yAːvad vaDUːvarayoːH guNameːlanaM na Bavati tAːvattu vivAːhaH na Bavati Kalu iti zam.
7_1861 veːtAːla vikramAːdityam abravI:t - BUːpateː ! mAːrgeː gacCan BavAːn eːkAːM kaTAːM zruNoːtu .
7_1862 kaliwgadeːzeː yajYasoːmanAːmAː eːkaH kulI:noː dvijaH vasati sma .
7_1863 tasya soːmadattAː nAːma BAːryAː AːsI:t .
7_1864 tayoːH deːvasvAːmI: nAːma eːkaH sutoː$Bavat .
7_1865 bAːlyakAːleː eːva sa svaguNEːH prasidDimalaBata .
7_1866 paraM yuvAːvasTAːyAːmeːva sa paYcatvaM gataH .
7_1867 zoːkAːkulOː BUːtvAː tasya mAːtAː pitAː ca uccEːH akrandatAːm .
7_1868 sarveː bAːnDavAːH agnisaMskAːrAːya deːvasvAːminaH zavaM zmazAːnamanayan .
7_1869 tatra vasan eːkAː ziva nAːmAː vRdDaH taM zoːBanAːkRtiM mRtaM brAːhmaNaputram apazyat .
7_1870 taM dRSqvAː saH vRdDaH mahAːntaM kleːzam anvaBavat acintayacca - mama kaleːvaraM jI:rNaM vartateː .
7_1871 yadi eːtat kaleːvaraM parityajya aham eːtasya brAːhmaNayuvakasya zarI:raM pravizeːyaM tahi ahaM aBI:SqasidDiM prAːptuM samarToː Baveːyam .
7_1872 eːtad vicAːrya praTamaM sa vRdDaH krandanamakaroːt tadantaraM sa anRtyat .
7_1873 yaTAː BujawgaH nirmoːkaM tyajati taTEːva sa vRdDaH svakaleːvaram atyajat dvijaputrasya ca zarI:raM prAːvizat .
7_1874 tadAː sa yuvAː brAːhmaNaputraH sajI:voː BUːtvAː udatiSVat .
7_1875 svaputraM jI:vitaM dRSqvAː pitAː ca sarveː bAːnDavAːH prasI:dan .
7_1876 deːvasvAːmI: svapitaraM banDUːn cAːkaTayat - ahaM saMsAːraM tyaktvAː saMnyAːsam awgI:kartumicCAːmi.
7_1877 eːtat zrutvAː tasya pitAː sarveː ca bAːnDavAːH zoːkAːkulAːH aBavan .
7_1878 paraM tEːH prAːrTyamAːnoː$pi deːvasvAːmI: eːtAːM kaTAːM zrAːvayitvAː veːtAːlaH vikramAːdityam apRcCat - rAːjan .
7_1879 vadatu BavAːn kimarTaM saH vRdDaH akrandat kimarTaM ca anRtyat.
7_1880 vikramAːdityaH udatarat - zrUːyatAːm atra kAːraNam .
7_1881 idaM zarI:raMm atyantalAːlitaM cirasaMgataM ca vartateː .
7_1882 bAːlyeː idaM zarI:raM tyajAːmI:ti cintayitvAː sa akrandat .
7_1883 paraM brAːhmaNaputrasya nUːtanaM zarI:raM pravizya ahaM sidDiM labDvAː kRtAːrToː BaviSyAːmi iti vicintya sa anRtyat.
7_1884 vikramAːdityasyeːdam uttaraM zrutvAː veːtAːlaH punaH ziMzipAːtaruM gatvAː tatra lalambeː .
7_1885 gawgAː parvata-rAːja-himAːlayAːt praBavati .
7_1886 eːSAː sarvAːsu nadI:Su zreːSVAː pavitratamAː ca asssti .
7_1887 gawgAːyAːH udBava-viSayeː eːkAː kaTAː asti .
7_1888 BagI:raTaH nAːma nRpaH pUːrvajAːnAːm udDAːrAːya tapasyAːm akaroːt tapasyAːyAːH ca praBAːveːNa saH gawgAːm svargAːt DarAːyAːm avatAːrayitum samarTaH aBavat .
7_1889 ataH eːva imAːm janAːH BAːgI:rAːaTI: iti api kaTayanti .
7_1890 teː asyAːH jalam atyaDikam pAːvanam mantanteː .
7_1891 bahavaH zradDAːlu-janAːH pratidinam asyAːm snAːnam kurvanti imAːm ca pUːjayanti .
7_1892 asyAːH taqeː haridvAːra-RSikeːSa-prayAːga-vAːrAːNasI:-ityAːdI:ni aneːkAːni tI:rTa-sTAːnAːni santi .
7_1893 prati-varSam puNyeːSu parvasu lakSAːNi janAːH eːSu tI:rTa-sTAːneːSu Aːgatya asyAːH pAːvana-jaleːna snAːnam kRtvAː duritAːni dUːrI:-kurvanti .
7_1894 yantrakAːrAːH asyAːH jalam avarudDya seːtum badDvAː mahAː-jalAːSayeːSu jala-saYcayam kurvanti .
7_1895 eːvam prakAːreːNa saYcitam jalam kSeːtrAːNAːm siYcanAːya upayujyateː .
7_1896 aneːna BUːmiH urvarAː Bavatti praBUːtam ca annam utpAːdayati .
7_1897 eːvam gawgAːyAːH jalam kRSeːH mahAːntam upakAːram karoːti .
7_1898 iyam dUːradarzana-DvanivistAːraka-zI:taka-ityAːdI:ni yantrAːNi saYcAːlayati viviDAːnAːm ca paNyAːnAːm vastUːnAːm nirmAːNeː sahAːyikAː Bavati .
7_1899 eːvam gawgAː loːkam paraloːkam ca uBayam api upakaroːti .
7_1900 tadantaraM tasya loːkaraYjanaH paramateːjasvI: sutoː$BUːta .
7_1901 sa dI:rGakAːyaH AːsI:t .
7_1902 sa eːva sutaH paramaM tapastaptvAː mahAːtapAːH daDI:ciH iti nAːmnAː prasidDiM labDavAːn .
7_1903 zakraH mahAːtapasaH daDI:ceːH satataM viBeːti sma .
7_1904 saH mahAːtapasaH daDI:ceːH tapoːBawgaM kartum aneːkavAːraM prAːyatata .
7_1905 tasminneːva kAːleː vRtrapramuKAːH kAːleːyAː nAːma dAːnavAː deːvAːn pI:xiyAːmAːsuH .
7_1906 zakrapramuKAː deːvAː vRtrAːsuram anyAːn ca dAːnavAːn nihantuM nAːzaknuvan .
7_1907 teːSAːM vaDayoːgyaM praharaNam anveːSquM zakraH trI:n loːkAːn vicacAːra paraM teːna tAːdRzaM praharaNaM noːpalabDam .
7_1908 tadAː indraH naranAːrAːyaNAːByAːM saha brahmaNaH samI:paM jagAːma .
7_1909 sa svakI:yaM dAːnavaBayaM brahmaNeː niveːdayAːmAːsa dAːnavAːnAːM ca vaDasya upAːyaM prapacCa .
7_1910 tatoː brahmAː zakramavoːcat- maharSeːH daDI:ceːH samI:paM gacCa .
7_1911 asOː RSizreːSVaH BavadBiH sarvEːH deːvEːH eːvaMprakAːreːNa yAːcyatAːm -heː daDI:ceː ! asmaByaM svakI:yAːni asTI:ni deːhi .
7_1912 deːvAːnAːM zilpI: tvaSqAː daDI:ceːH asTiBiH asurAːNAːM vRtrasya ca vaDoːpayoːgI:ni praharaNAːni vajraM ca nirmAːsyati .
7_1913 yadAː RSiH daDI:ciH eːvaM yAːcitaH tadAːsOː atiprasannOː BUːtvAː svakI:yaM jI:vanaM tapazca saPalamamanyata .
7_1914 trayAːNAːM loːkAːNAːM kalyAːNaM manasi niDAːya asOː zI:Grameːva svaprAːNAːn tyaktavAːn .
7_1915 prahRSqamanAːH zakraH tAːni asTI:ni AːdAːya deːvAːnAːM zilpinaH tvaSquH sakAːzaM jagAːma .
7_1916 tvaSqAː tEːH asTiBiH viviDAːni divyAːni AːyuDAːni vajraM ca nirmameː .
7_1917 eːtAːni divyAːni praharaNAːni vajraM ca AːdAːya zakraH deːvEːH saha kAːleːyAːKyAːn asurAːn prati prayAːNamakaroːt.
7_1918 saH dAːnavEːH aBirakSitaM dyAːvAːpRTivI: ca AːvRtya tiSVantaM vRtrAːsuram AːyuDEːH AːcakrAːma .
7_1919 tadAː dAːnavEːH saha zakrAːdI:nAːM deːvAːnAːM tumulaM yudDaM prAːvartata .
7_1920 sarveː loːkAː akampanta .
7_1921 eːvaMBUːteː deːvAːsurasaMgrAːmeː viSNuteːjasAː AːviSqaH zakraH vRtrasya zirasi vajram apAːtayat .
7_1922 teːna vajreːNa vRtrasya ziroː BagnaM saMjAːtaM BUːmOː cAːpatat .
7_1923 sarveː asurAːH vyanazyan deːvAːzca zAːntiM prAːpnuvan .
7_1924 ayameːva heːtuH yat zakraH vRtrahAː iti saMjYAːM labDavAːn .
7_1925 vRtrasya dAːnavAːnAːM ca nAːzaM vinAː jagati zAːntiH sTAːpayitum azakyAː AːsI:t .
7_1926 eːtasya mahataH tyAːgasya kRteː daDI:ciH nAːma jagati sadEːva sTAːsyati .
7_1927 ayam utsavaH kAːrtikamAːsAːsya amAːvasyAːyAːM Bavati .
