8_2391 vara: atra samI:pasTeː grAːmeː nivasati.
8_2392 vivAːhaviSayakavAːrtAːlAːpAːrTam eːva AːvAːByAːM tasya gRhaM prati gamyateː aDunAː.
8_2393 maDyeː BAːgyavazAːt svarNAːmbikAːyAː: darzanaBAːgyaM prAːptam.
